message: /* 'Best Of Best' Naver Music Awards */Naver Music Awards is legitimate, they started on 2016 and discontinued on 2017, listing the Top10 on their chart in a certain year + the Top10 Most Love Artist. You can see an article about 2017 Naver Music Awards on Soompi with getting accolades.\nBugs 20th Anniversary Awards gives trophies as recognition, some of the artist such Taeyeon shared an acceptance speech for the same awards too, it was called an award for a reason.
